<p class="opening">@PageData("description")</p>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<p>Looking to the past helps shape our future in many ways. We can learn from its mistakes and improve upon it. As the new year slowly takes shape, we are beginning to see which trends are setting the tone for this year. Many of them are familiar, while a few offer thrilling new aspects to try. Here you will find five of the most prominent trends that we believe will impact 2018.  </p>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<p><strong>RICH COLORS</strong></p>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<div align="center" class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <a href="http://timothywhealon.com/Project/Upper%20East%20Side%20Duplex" target="_blank">
