            <img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="~/images/Trends-2018Predictions-RichColor9.jpg">
        </a>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<p>Deep, dense extravagant colors create a lush palette for our homes once again this year. Moving away from the all neutral color schemes, 2018 is all about being bold. Pushing the boundaries to create a chic space full of life and color. Pairing vibrant with pastel, saturated with muted, the color rich trend of this year also embraces the harmony between opposites. Layering bright shades with soft hues creates a more natural surrounding, one of welcoming enjoyment.  </p>
