<p><strong>BIG AND BOLD</strong></p>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<div align="center"><a href="http://www.laurenliess.com/BlogRetrieve.aspx?PostID=1011013&A=SearchResult&SearchID=4870159&ObjectID=1011013&ObjectType=55" target="_blank"><img class="img-responsive" alt="" src="~/images/Trends-2018Predictions-BigBold1.jpg"></a></div>
<div class="spacer"></div>

<p>From dramatic to playful, big and bold prints are scaling their way to the top in 2018. Feminine florals, cheeky motifs, and abstract patterns are all making a distinct impression. Monotonous, neutral filled rooms are falling out of favor for livelier, eye-catching spaces. High contrast or subdued schemes, both make a statement in any space. Perfect for the dreamer in all of us, these designs are motivating us to seek joy in happy prints and gleeful colors. </p>
